Preheat grill to medium-high heat. Pierce potatoes with fork or small sharp knife. Rub with oil; sprinkle with salt. Place potatoes on microwaveable plate. Microwave on HIGH 8 min. or until tender, turning after 4 min. Place potatoes on greased grate of grill. Cook 12 to 15 min. or until potatoes are crisp and browned, turning occasionally. Split potatoes. Serve topped with remaining ingredients.